data.description: BACK ON THE MARKET! BACK ON THE MARKET! BACK ON THE MARKET! WHAT AN OPPORTUNITY THIS IS! DON'T MISS OUT! Move-in Ready 2 large bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, 2 car garage. Large family room, GREAT sunroom, granite counters in the kitchen, interior painted in 2022. Front porch and covered back patio with storage shed, chain link fence, and grassy area with an auto sprinkler. Dreamland Villa is a 55+ community on a County Island. The community offers an optional membership for an annual fee to join. For the members, there are swimming pools and hot tubs at 2 locations, lots of activities, entertainment, and socials. Please visit the Dreamland Villa website for information on Community Services!
